task.summary: ## 0.2.0 * Added function: init() socket (please call this function before doing anything with socket)
- release version 0.3.3 * Fixed bugs: iOS don't create new SocketManger (with the same domain) if it already existed.
## 0.4.0 * Added: The guide for installing this plugin on iOS * Added: MIT LICENSE
## 0.4.1 * Changed: changed android dependency from "com.github.nkzawa:socket.io-client:0.3.0" to official socket.io "io.socket:socket.io-client:1.0.0"
